      "para_id": "Q001460.2",
      "line_range": "2",
      "translation": "(i 1') ... he šhose ... by eₓtispišy ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001460.3",
      "line_range": "3",
      "translation": "(i 2') For the kind protective spirit , Ninsumun , his personal deity , he built her house in Iri-kug ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001460.8",
      "line_range": "8",
      "translation": "(i 7') ... Zazaru ...."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001460.11",
      "line_range": "11",
      "translation": "(ii 1') For Urnunta-ea , child of Ninĝirsu , he built her house in Iri-kug ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001460.15",
      "line_range": "15",
      "translation": "(ii 5') For Ninmarki , the kind woman , he chose the šita - abba-priest by extispicy ."
    }
  ],
